<topic id="topic_zvx_jd2_5h">
  <title>Impose Custom Options for Writers</title>
  <body>
    <section>
      <title>Question</title>
      <p>How to enable <uicontrol>Track Changes</uicontrol> at startup?</p>
    </section>
    <section>
      <title>Answer</title>
      <p>There are two ways to enable <uicontrol>Track Changes</uicontrol> for every document that
        you open:</p>
      <p>
        <ol id="ol_up4_d22_5h">
          <li>You could <xref
              href="http://www.oxygenxml.com/doc/ug-editor/topics/default-options.html"
              format="html" scope="external" product="editor">customise the default
              options</xref><xref
              href="http://www.oxygenxml.com/doc/ug-editorEclipse/topics/default-options.html"
              format="html" scope="external" product="editorEclipse">customise the default
              options</xref><xref
              href="http://www.oxygenxml.com/doc/ug-author/topics/default-options.html"
              format="html" scope="external" product="author">customise the default
              options</xref><xref
              href="http://www.oxygenxml.com/doc/ug-authorEclipse/topics/default-options.html"
              format="html" scope="external" product="authorEclipse">customise the default
              options</xref><ph product="sdk">customise the default options</ph> which are
            used by your writers and set the Track Changes <xref
              href="http://www.oxygenxml.com/doc/ug-editor/topics/preferences-track-changes.html"
              format="html" scope="external" product="editor"><codeph>Initial State</codeph>
              option</xref><xref
              href="http://www.oxygenxml.com/doc/ug-editorEclipse/topics/preferences-track-changes.html"
              format="html" scope="external" product="editorEclipse"><codeph>Initial State</codeph>
              option</xref><xref
              href="http://www.oxygenxml.com/doc/ug-author/topics/preferences-track-changes.html"
              format="html" scope="external" product="author"><codeph>Initial State</codeph>
              option</xref><xref
              href="http://www.oxygenxml.com/doc/ug-authorEclipse/topics/preferences-track-changes.html"
              format="html" scope="external" product="authorEclipse"><codeph>Initial State</codeph>
              option</xref><ph product="sdk"><codeph>Initial State</codeph> option</ph> to
              <codeph>Always On.</codeph></li>
          <li>Use the API to toggle the Track Changes state after a document is opened in
              <uicontrol>Author</uicontrol>
            mode:<codeblock outputclass="language-java">// Check the current state of Track Changes 
boolean trackChangesOn = authorAccess.getReviewController().isTrackingChanges();
if (!trackChangesOn) {
  // Set Track Changes state to On
  authorAccess.getReviewController().toggleTrackChanges();
}</codeblock></li>
        </ol>
      </p>
    </section>
  </body>
